      "rationale": "Material property inputs were derived from coupon tensile tests on the same production lot as the tested constructs. Geometric inputs were measured by CMM on each individual construct. The UQ campaign quantified input uncertainty distributions and propagated them through the model, confirming that elastic modulus and yield strength are the dominant drivers of QoI variability."
