    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for medium model risk. The single deficiency (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is acknowledged and documented. The ensemble modeling approach, strong inter-laboratory agreement, and favorable E/uval metrics across all three QoIs provide sufficient overall credibility evidence to support the Accepted decision for this medium-risk, medium-consequence COU. The uncertainty quantification campaign results, including parameter sensitivity rankings documented in NRJ-UQ-2024-01, further support confidence in the model predictions.",
